    <p>{`To prevent bot (automatic program that act like a human without being a real one) to register account to your website, you can use what we can captcha. Captcha is image that only human can read. They have letters that need to be input in a text box when the form is filled up. Today, I'll show you how to implement ReCaptcha, a popular Captcha service that is totally free and owned by Google.`}</p>
